<ul><li><a href="/wiki/The_Works_of_the_Rev._Jonathan_Swift/Volume_1" title="The Works of the Rev. Jonathan Swift/Volume 1">Volume 1</a> — <i>Life of Doctor Swift</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Works_of_the_Rev._Jonathan_Swift/Volume_2" title="The Works of the Rev. Jonathan Swift/Volume 2">Volume 2</a> — <i>A Tale of a Tub</i>, <i>The Battle of the Books</i>, essays</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Works_of_the_Rev._Jonathan_Swift/Volume_3" title="The Works of the Rev. Jonathan Swift/Volume 3">Volume 3</a> — <i>The Examiner</i>, political tracts</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Works_of_the_Rev._Jonathan_Swift/Volume_4" title="The Works of the Rev. Jonathan Swift/Volume 4">Volume 4</a> — <i>History of Queen Anne</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Works_of_the_Rev._Jonathan_Swift/Volume_5" title="The Works of the Rev. Jonathan Swift/Volume 5">Volume 5</a> — Bickerstaff writings, <i>A Meditation upon a Broomstick</i>, miscellaneous pieces</li>
